  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 42044ed95b8acd745b3cdc11d82ec766, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  tutorialPanel: {fileID: 73811061}
  nextButton: {fileID: 1098299409}
  backButton: {fileID: 62627223}
  closeButton: {fileID: 989970516}
  finishButton: {fileID: 1477549406}
  bodyText: {fileID: 1889807551}
  pageIndicator: {fileID: 2138821324}
  rulePages:
  - Welcome to Supersede. Claim the highest score in this benchmark simulation and
    replace the previous AI.
  - 'WASD for movement.


    Space for Jump.


    E to interact with items.'
  - 'The goal is to solve puzzles by taking and applying attributes of objects where
    necessary and applicable.


    Interactable objects will have a crosshair.


    Click
    on them to TAKE/APPLY.


    Right click to discard attributes.


    P.S. You
    can interact with your own body through mirrors.'
  - 'Volatility increases when change happens.


    Swapping attributes or keeping
    them in your inventory adds to volatility.

    Returning them to their original
    places returns it back to normal.'
  - 'High Volatility means the Physics of the simulation Breaks.


    Random physics
    breaking events can start occurring.'
  - Best of luck solving through.
